1
00:00:15,580 --> 00:00:19,620
Wow, that shot just now
was insane!

2
00:00:19,840 --> 00:00:21,179
That's Naoya for you.

3
00:00:21,180 --> 00:00:22,850
Hey, make way for Naoya-san!

4
00:00:22,890 --> 00:00:24,930
Seriously, no one else
could make a shot like that.

5
00:00:24,980 --> 00:00:26,416
Naoya-san,
I'll follow you for the rest of my life!

6
00:00:26,440 --> 00:00:27,150
Please let me!

7
00:00:27,151 --> 00:00:28,320
Yeah, yeah, I get it.

8
00:00:29,920 --> 00:00:31,440
Wow, he's so cool!

9
00:00:31,520 --> 00:00:32,720
I wish I could play like that.

10
00:00:44,720 --> 00:00:46,060
Takaaki.

11
00:00:47,120 --> 00:00:48,799
Are you still Naoya's errand boy?

12
00:00:48,800 --> 00:00:51,000
How about running an errand for us too?

13
00:00:51,220 --> 00:00:53,220
If we take just one,
he probably won't even notice.

14
00:00:57,400 --> 00:00:58,720
Hey, cut it out!

15
00:00:59,200 --> 00:01:01,999
He's been trained so well
that he only listens to Naoya.

16
00:01:02,000 --> 00:01:04,139
What do you mean, "trained"?

17
00:01:04,140 --> 00:01:05,340
Hey, let's go, let's go.

18
00:01:05,690 --> 00:01:07,059
I don't want to get
into a fight with Naoya.

19
00:01:07,060 --> 00:01:08,060
Fine, fine.

20
00:02:02,060 --> 00:02:03,540
What took you so long?

21
00:02:03,880 --> 00:02:05,080
I almost fell asleep.

22
00:02:06,440 --> 00:02:07,440
I'm sorry.

23
00:02:11,540 --> 00:02:13,340
Ah! I dropped that on the floor.

24
00:02:16,040 --> 00:02:17,420
Whoa!

25
00:02:18,930 --> 00:02:20,470
Even my feet are soaked.

26
00:02:22,320 --> 00:02:23,320
Here.

27
00:02:26,100 --> 00:02:27,180
Lick it clean.

28
00:02:35,760 --> 00:02:36,860
Understood.

29
00:02:54,840 --> 00:02:57,380
You really do
whatever I say, don't you?

30
00:03:11,120 --> 00:03:12,120
Hey.

31
00:03:12,780 --> 00:03:13,780
This hairstyle.

32
00:03:14,180 --> 00:03:16,060
It's exactly the same
as it was in high school.

33
00:03:17,320 --> 00:03:18,400
Yeah.

34
00:03:22,020 --> 00:03:23,020
You know...

35
00:03:24,950 --> 00:03:27,320
It's about time we end this relationship.

36
00:04:35,500 --> 00:04:38,700
"The Servant Prince"
(Episode 1)

37
00:04:40,500 --> 00:04:45,500
(A few days ago)

38
00:04:58,000 --> 00:05:00,900
I was put in charge of running
a subsidiary of my parents' company.

39
00:05:02,600 --> 00:05:04,380
But I ruined it two years ago.

40
00:05:08,010 --> 00:05:09,010
Oh.

41
00:05:12,340 --> 00:05:15,520
Having lost all trust and status,
I'm now just unemployed.

42
00:05:25,740 --> 00:05:26,950
By contrast...

43
00:05:29,400 --> 00:05:30,400
Lick it clean.

44
00:05:31,620 --> 00:05:32,620
Understood.

45
00:05:33,500 --> 00:05:34,830
Takaaki, on the other hand,

46
00:05:43,580 --> 00:05:45,669
succeeded by developing an app.

47
00:05:45,670 --> 00:05:47,530
Now, he's the CEO of a startup.

48
00:06:06,900 --> 00:06:07,900
Yeah.

49
00:06:08,780 --> 00:06:11,160
An elite couple. They
look so good together.

50
00:06:13,580 --> 00:06:16,100
Compared to our high school days,
it's unimaginable.

51
00:06:16,880 --> 00:06:20,460
Our social standings
have completely reversed.

52
00:06:33,660 --> 00:06:36,770
Damn it. What am I
running away from?

53
00:06:47,400 --> 00:06:48,700
This is pathetic...

54
00:07:06,630 --> 00:07:07,760
Excuse me.

55
00:07:09,720 --> 00:07:12,290
I've decided not to
get a haircut after all.

56
00:07:12,840 --> 00:07:14,400
No haircut?

57
00:07:15,260 --> 00:07:16,820
Then how would you like me to style it?

58
00:07:19,160 --> 00:07:21,870
Please just dye the underlayer.

59
00:07:22,960 --> 00:07:24,250
The underlayer, got it.

60
00:07:25,060 --> 00:07:27,690
I'll go prepare the dye.
Please wait a moment.

61
00:07:34,220 --> 00:07:36,330
Watching him constantly change,

62
00:07:39,750 --> 00:07:41,320
while I remain exactly the same.

63
00:07:51,980 --> 00:07:54,920
Even though he no longer
needs to follow my orders,

64
00:07:55,420 --> 00:07:59,200
Takaaki still comes whenever I call,
cooking for me like this,

65
00:07:59,560 --> 00:08:00,760
cleaning my place,

66
00:08:01,700 --> 00:08:02,700
and then...

67
00:08:03,400 --> 00:08:05,080
Forget about that.
Come over here.

68
00:08:07,700 --> 00:08:08,800
Let's do it.

69
00:08:10,360 --> 00:08:11,460
Understood.

70
00:08:15,060 --> 00:08:18,940
Having sex with me on command.

71
00:08:46,900 --> 00:08:49,120
Takaaki has a bright future ahead of him.

72
00:08:50,280 --> 00:08:54,130
If only I could stop craving him...

73
00:09:01,120 --> 00:09:02,320
I'm going to take a shower.

74
00:09:03,940 --> 00:09:05,040
Understood.

75
00:09:22,860 --> 00:09:23,860
Hey.

76
00:09:24,160 --> 00:09:25,160
This hairstyle.

77
00:09:25,480 --> 00:09:27,360
It's exactly the same
as it was in high school.

78
00:09:28,720 --> 00:09:29,720
Yeah.

79
00:09:39,040 --> 00:09:40,040
You know...

80
00:09:42,410 --> 00:09:44,330
It's about time we end this relationship.

81
00:09:53,160 --> 00:09:54,380
What do you mean?

82
00:09:55,040 --> 00:09:56,040
I mean all of this.

83
00:09:57,260 --> 00:09:58,740
I won't ask you to come over anymore.

84
00:09:59,280 --> 00:10:00,680
And you shouldn't come back either.

85
00:10:05,760 --> 00:10:06,760
Understood.

86
00:10:14,900 --> 00:10:16,490
Leave the key.

87
00:10:21,420 --> 00:10:22,420
Understood.

88
00:11:07,200 --> 00:11:08,520
Seriously.

89
00:11:10,180 --> 00:11:11,930
He's always so obedient.

90
00:11:23,050 --> 00:11:24,906
- You worked hard.
- Sixty-eight points.

91
00:11:24,930 --> 00:11:26,579
That score is way too low!

92
00:11:26,580 --> 00:11:27,619
Don't laugh at me!

93
00:11:27,620 --> 00:11:28,820
It really is super low.

94
00:11:30,000 --> 00:11:32,280
Growing up, even though I was
always surrounded by people,

95
00:11:33,020 --> 00:11:35,460
there was no one I could truly trust.

96
00:11:37,600 --> 00:11:39,350
Even the subsidiary I was put in charge of

97
00:11:41,020 --> 00:11:44,520
had already been set up to fail
by an opposing faction.

98
00:11:46,240 --> 00:11:48,760
By the time I realized it,
it was already too late.

99
00:11:51,260 --> 00:11:53,060
I've always been all alone.

100
00:12:07,320 --> 00:12:09,390
It's only been two weeks since then.

101
00:12:10,700 --> 00:12:11,840
Only two weeks.

102
00:12:14,130 --> 00:12:17,040
If I don't call him,
he won't show up.

103
00:12:22,510 --> 00:12:23,510
Bartender.

104
00:12:23,690 --> 00:12:25,030
Another one of these, please.

105
00:12:35,490 --> 00:12:38,060
Hey, are you alone?

106
00:12:43,010 --> 00:12:43,760
Are you okay?

107
00:12:43,761 --> 00:12:45,190
Yeah, I'm fine.

108
00:12:45,540 --> 00:12:46,550
We're here.

109
00:12:47,530 --> 00:12:50,140
Wow, amazing. It's so spacious.

110
00:13:28,550 --> 00:13:29,560
What's wrong?

111
00:13:30,550 --> 00:13:31,550
Sorry.

112
00:13:32,870 --> 00:13:35,330
I'm not feeling very well.

113
00:13:35,670 --> 00:13:36,560
I'm going home.

114
00:13:36,561 --> 00:13:38,330
Hey, wait... wait a minute.

115
00:13:43,190 --> 00:13:44,190
Ah...

116
00:13:45,030 --> 00:13:46,520
I'm such an idiot.

117
00:13:48,690 --> 00:13:49,690
Exactly.

118
00:13:50,080 --> 00:13:55,010
Surprisingly, other than Takaaki,

119
00:13:55,530 --> 00:13:57,270
I've never even kissed anyone else.

120
00:14:26,330 --> 00:14:31,530
Since high school, whether it was academics,
sports, socializing, or relationships,

121
00:14:32,160 --> 00:14:33,640
I handled everything with ease.

122
00:14:35,810 --> 00:14:38,350
Just maintaining that perfect image
took everything I had.

123
00:14:42,770 --> 00:14:43,870
I'm home.

124
00:14:47,070 --> 00:14:48,350
Naoya.

125
00:14:50,570 --> 00:14:53,200
You must rank first in the school
on the next mock exam.

126
00:14:54,680 --> 00:14:56,179
Only because you promised
to do what's expected of you

127
00:14:56,180 --> 00:14:57,870
do I tolerate you looking like that.

128
00:15:03,270 --> 00:15:04,270
Yes.

129
00:15:27,970 --> 00:15:32,800
It can be written in the form of k plus two
and k plus one-third, right?

130
00:15:34,560 --> 00:15:35,680
I see.

131
00:15:38,930 --> 00:15:40,110
Hey, Takaaki.

132
00:15:41,630 --> 00:15:42,630
On the next mock exam,

133
00:15:42,770 --> 00:15:44,250
let me get first place.

134
00:15:48,070 --> 00:15:49,070
Understood.

135
00:15:53,339 --> 00:15:54,365
Naoya Goto

136
00:15:55,325 --> 00:15:57,072
[First place at school
and in the East district]

137
00:16:13,932 --> 00:16:15,432
Takaaki Sato

138
00:16:16,499 --> 00:16:18,265
[Second place in the
East district and at school]

139
00:16:20,710 --> 00:16:21,830
What the...

140
00:16:23,230 --> 00:16:26,770
I always came in second.
So it was all because of him.

141
00:16:33,200 --> 00:16:36,880
Looking back, maybe I
admired him back then.

142
00:16:38,950 --> 00:16:40,120
Takaaki.

143
00:17:13,520 --> 00:17:14,790
Excuse me.

144
00:17:15,770 --> 00:17:18,280
CEO, tomorrow's schedule
has been confirmed.

145
00:17:19,010 --> 00:17:21,390
At 10:00 AM, there's the regular meeting.

146
00:17:21,590 --> 00:17:25,089
Regarding the additional financing, the
documents have been shared to the knowledge base.

147
00:17:25,090 --> 00:17:26,589
I see. Thank you.

148
00:17:26,590 --> 00:17:30,270
At 2:00 PM, there's the debugging
report for the new feature.

149
00:17:30,410 --> 00:17:31,806
You can review it while you're on the move.

150
00:17:31,830 --> 00:17:33,550
- That's all.
- Understood.

151
00:17:34,770 --> 00:17:35,770
By the way,

152
00:17:35,970 --> 00:17:37,850
how is the matter with
Goto Construction going?

153
00:17:38,490 --> 00:17:39,570
Ah, yes.

154
00:17:40,750 --> 00:17:43,780
The list of key personnel
and clients is ready.

155
00:17:43,830 --> 00:17:46,270
The details of that matter
are also being compiled.

156
00:17:46,810 --> 00:17:47,970
- Thank you.
- Yes, sir.

157
00:17:49,290 --> 00:17:52,440
But why do you want to look into
Goto Construction's internal data?

158
00:17:53,070 --> 00:17:55,910
To be ready to take action at any moment,
we need to prepare in advance.

159
00:17:56,110 --> 00:17:57,110
Pardon?

160
00:17:58,570 --> 00:18:02,590
I mean, as soon as I receive the order,
I can act immediately.

161
00:18:03,410 --> 00:18:05,160
Ah... order?

162
00:18:05,210 --> 00:18:06,460
I'm leaving for the day.

163
00:18:07,250 --> 00:18:08,250
I'll leave the rest to you.

164
00:18:08,251 --> 00:18:10,520
Ah, yes. Understood.

165
00:18:34,080 --> 00:18:35,380
Bartender, another one.

166
00:18:41,020 --> 00:18:42,200
Are you okay?

167
00:18:43,870 --> 00:18:45,680
Shall we go somewhere we can rest?

168
00:18:46,740 --> 00:18:48,320
Who the hell are you, old man?

169
00:18:49,520 --> 00:18:51,720
Whatever, it doesn't matter who you are.

170
00:18:53,480 --> 00:18:57,300
Since you're this drunk,
it doesn't matter who does it, right?

171
00:18:57,380 --> 00:18:58,380
Is it your first time?

172
00:18:58,880 --> 00:18:59,880
Is your place nearby?

173
00:19:04,680 --> 00:19:05,950
Takaaki.

174
00:19:07,980 --> 00:19:09,490
What are you doing here?

175
00:19:10,310 --> 00:19:13,320
By the way, where's your girlfriend?

176
00:19:13,740 --> 00:19:14,740
Girlfriend?

177
00:19:16,480 --> 00:19:17,840
More importantly, Naoya,

178
00:19:17,860 --> 00:19:20,020
would you rather be held
by a guy like that than by me?

179
00:19:25,040 --> 00:19:27,680
Why do you think
I let you go in the first place?

180
00:19:32,540 --> 00:19:37,080
Please, you have to be happy.

181
00:19:57,730 --> 00:19:58,750
Understood.

182
00:20:09,000 --> 00:20:10,830
Ouch...

183
00:20:14,100 --> 00:20:15,170
Are you okay?

184
00:20:23,080 --> 00:20:24,220
Why are you here?

185
00:20:26,720 --> 00:20:28,530
Didn't I tell you not to come back?

186
00:20:32,600 --> 00:20:34,720
Because you told me to be happy.

187
00:20:35,560 --> 00:20:36,580
Huh?

188
00:20:43,340 --> 00:20:45,660
It's only been two weeks,
and your place is full of trash.

189
00:20:46,540 --> 00:20:51,000
And in the end, you were even about to
spread your legs for a man like that.

190
00:21:16,000 --> 00:21:18,020
I never told you to do that.

191
00:21:18,480 --> 00:21:19,480
Yeah.

192
00:21:19,780 --> 00:21:21,750
I did it because I wanted to.

193
00:21:25,360 --> 00:21:27,739
The sex when I'm in control
won't be as gentle as before.

194
00:21:27,740 --> 00:21:28,760
You'd better be prepared.

195
00:21:31,180 --> 00:21:34,159
Don't you have a girlfriend?

196
00:21:34,160 --> 00:21:35,680
I don't know what you saw,

197
00:21:36,790 --> 00:21:39,480
but in business, a professional
smile is always necessary.

198
00:21:52,580 --> 00:21:53,580
Huh?

199
00:21:57,620 --> 00:21:58,720
I am happy.

200
00:22:05,400 --> 00:22:06,680
Why would it be someone like me?

201
00:22:08,106 --> 00:22:12,466
Since high school, I'm the only
one who's been by your side, right?

202
00:22:21,560 --> 00:22:23,040
If you want,

203
00:22:24,340 --> 00:22:27,070
I can arrange the paperwork
for you to return to the company.

204
00:22:29,340 --> 00:22:31,630
If you want to destroy
the people who kicked you out,

205
00:22:31,760 --> 00:22:33,280
just give me the order.

206
00:22:36,300 --> 00:22:37,500
My happiness

207
00:22:39,690 --> 00:22:41,870
is granting your wishes.

208
00:22:47,080 --> 00:22:48,090
So, what is your command?

209
00:22:58,750 --> 00:22:59,880
Forever...

210
00:23:03,090 --> 00:23:04,650
Stay by my side forever.

211
00:24:29,900 --> 00:24:30,800
(Next Episode)

212
00:24:30,840 --> 00:24:32,379
You've got it all wrong.

213
00:24:32,380 --> 00:24:34,659
I've been waiting
for a long time now.

214
00:24:34,660 --> 00:24:37,540
Isn't that company name
the one I mentioned?

215
00:24:37,580 --> 00:24:39,170
It's just a brand-new startup.

216
00:24:39,340 --> 00:24:44,270
I'll never forgive the person
who pushed Naoya to the brink.
